sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Board as Tickets board
    participant API as Agent controller REST
    participant Storage as sessionStorage
    participant Router
    participant Chat as Chat component

    User->>Board: Open ticket, Prototype in chat
    Board->>API: GET /tickets/:id/prototype-prompt
    API-->>Board: { prompt }
    Board->>Storage: set agentConsole.chatDraft.v1
    Board->>Router: navigate /clients/:clientId/agents/:agentId
    Router->>Chat: activate route
    Chat->>Chat: onAgentSelect → reconnect socket
    Chat->>Storage: readAndClear draft
    Storage-->>Chat: message
    Chat->>Chat: chatMessage.set(message)

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Board as Tickets board
    participant API as Agent controller REST
    participant Socket as Clients WS / forward
    participant Manager as Agent manager
    participant Store as NgRx sockets

    User->>Board: Generate description
    Board->>API: POST body-generation-sessions
    API-->>Board: generationId
    Board->>Socket: connect + setClient + forward generateTicketBody
    Socket->>Manager: generateTicketBody
    Manager-->>Socket: ticketBodyResult
    Socket-->>Store: ticketBodyLastResult
    Store-->>Board: match correlationId
    Board->>API: POST apply-generated-body
    API-->>Board: updated ticket
    Board->>Board: reload list + detail
